                Segillus Iliat<lb break="no" n="2"/>i <expan><abbr>f</abbr><ex>ilius</ex></expan> et Abua Tapp<lb break="no" n="3"/>onis &amp;lt;f=E&amp;gt;(ilia) <lb n="4"/><expan><abbr>Seg</abbr><ex>illus</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>an</abbr><ex>norum</ex></expan> <lb n="5"/>L <expan><ex>h</ex><abbr>ic</abbr></expan> situs <lb n="6"/><expan><abbr>es</abbr><ex>t</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>fili</abbr><ex>i</ex></expan> posier<lb break="no" n="7"/>unt <note>sic</note> 
            </ab></div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>Oberhalb des Inschriftfeldes die Büsten einer Frau und eines Mannes. (B): CIL 03, 11302: Z. 1/2: Ilia[t]/i; Z. 2/3: Tap[p]/onis; CIL 03, 11302; Neumann: Z. 3: f(ilia); CIL 03, 11302: Z. 6: es[t]; Neumann: Z. 6: [e]s(t).</p>
